Bread Recipe

2 teaspoons of yeast
5 cups flour 
2-1/4th cup of warm water (110 F)
3 tablespoons sugar plus 1/2 teaspoon sugar
1 tablespoon of salt
6 cups flour

dissolve yeast and 1/2 teaspoon sugar in warm water; let stand until bubbles form on surface. 

Whisk together remaining 3 tablespoons sugar, salt and flour. pour into flour mixture and beat until smooth.

Let rise

Bake at 375Â° until golden brown and and knife comes out clean 
